---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <!-- ====== About Section ====== -->
  <section id="about" class="about-section dark-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="h1">MIDIverse Technologies</h1>
      <h2 class="h2 line">Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        At MIDIverse Technologies, we are passionate about bridging the gap
        between music and technology. Founded by a team of musicians, engineers,
        and developers, our mission is to create powerful, intuitive MIDI
        hardware and software tools that empower creators across the globe.
        Whether you’re a music producer, hobbyist, performer, or developer,
        MIDIverse is your gateway to the ßnext era of digital music innovation.
      </p>
      <p>
        We believe in open collaboration, modular design, and seamless
        integration with the tools you already use — and the ones you haven’t
        imagined yet.
      </p>
      <h2 class="h2 line">Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        To dissolve the boundaries between musical creativity and technological
        control, empowering creators with intuitive and powerful tools.
      </p>
      <h2 class="h2 line">Our Vision</h2>
      <p>
        To be at the forefront of MIDI innovation, creating an interconnected
        'MIDIverse' of hardware and software that fosters creativity and
        efficiency.
      </p>
      <p>
        🚀 To build a universe of intelligent MIDI tools that redefine how
        people interact with music, hardware, and software — from studio to
        stage and beyond.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="h2 line">🧠 The Leadership Team</h2>

    <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 my-12 mx-12">
      <li>
        <h3 class="text-xl">🎧 Alex Rivera</h3>
        <span class="text-sm">Founder & CEO</span>
        <p class="text-left mt-4">
          A multi-instrumentalist and engineer with over a decade of experience
          in music tech startups, Alex leads the company with a deep
          understanding of both sound and systems.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class="text-xl">🛠️ Lina Zhou</h3>
        <span class="text-sm">CTO & Head of Product Innovation</span>
        <p class="text-left mt-4">
          Lina drives our product development strategy, blending a background in
          embedded systems and creative AI to deliver cutting-edge music
          hardware.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class="text-xl">🌐 Marcus Silva</h3>
        <span class="text-sm">COO & Community Architect</span>
        <p class="text-left mt-4">
          Marcus ensures the heartbeat of MIDIverse stays aligned with the needs
          of our users, creators, and developer community. He also leads
          partnerships and global operations.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="h2">Contact</h2>
    <h3 class="h3 text-center">📬 Contact Information</h3>

    <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-12 mx-12">
